Moody’s Puts Nykredit Ratings on Review for Possible Downgrade

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-14T17:06:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/moody-s-puts-nykredit-ratings-on-review-for-possible-downgrade.html
Moody’s Investors Service placed
Nykredit Bank AS’s parent Nykredit Realkredit A/S’s A1 issuer
rating and Baa1 Tier 1 hybrid rating on review for possible
downgrade, the ratings service said in an e-mailed statement
today. The A1 long-term and P-1 short term debt and deposit
ratings and A3 junior subordinated ratings of Nykredit Bank have
also been placed on review for possible downgrade, the statement
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 